The paper focuses on the analysis of scientific output and research collaboration among the BRICS countries, which falls under the domain of computer science. Specifically, the study investigates the development of the BRICS countries in the domain of top-cited papers, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL), social and information networks (cs.SI), statistics (cs.ST), systems and control (cs.SY), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
